description:
A faster, better and more stable redis desktop manager.

A faster, better and more stable redis desktop manager [GUI client], compatible with Linux, Windows, Mac.
What's more, it won't crash when loading a large number of keys.
Change log:- 🔍 Search support when connections>=4
- 🟢 Connections status show
- ⚓ Filter support in memory analysis
- 📃 HEX_FILE support in custom viewer
- ✔️ Bug fix
- ♾️ UI optimize
